00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,520
to take care of me

291
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,880
and I went to Singapore

292
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:57,800
to look after my mom who had a car accident

293
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,800
after graduating from high school.

294
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:00,680
At least

295
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:01,600
I myself don't think

296
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,930
this experience can be called wonderful.

297
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:06,860
Well...

298
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,120
Ling Xiao?

299
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:29,940
Hello, Mom.

300
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:30,840
Ling Xiao,

301
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,320
I'm looking for

302
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,960
the pineapple tart store near your university.

303
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,480
Where the hell is it?

304
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,560
Take a turn

305
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,400
from the beef noodle restaurant at the interaction,

306
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:40,460
and you will see it.

307
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:42,920
OK, I got it.

308
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:44,120
Fine, I'm hanging up.

309
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:44,760
Goodbye.

310
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:58,380
[Xiaomei]

311
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:03,160
Hello?

312
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:04,920
What's up?

313
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,089
How is Mom recently?

314
00:17:07,349 --> 00:17:08,480
She's just as usual.

315
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,020
What else could she be?

316
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,589
But she's

317
00:17:11,589 --> 00:17:12,720
a little better now.

318
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,599
She seems to be in a good mood.

319
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,589
Yesterday she invited her friends to dinner,

320
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:19,200
and she goes shopping today.

321
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:22,210
She's almost spent all of the family fortune.

322
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:24,760
You are on holiday, right?

323
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,440
Don't provoke her at home.

324
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,640
Behave yourself,

325
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,560
and don't go out

326
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:29,720
playing with your classmates every day.

327
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,600
You got that?

328
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:33,120
I got it! Stop nagging.

329
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:35,320
How about you try and take care of her?

330
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:35,880
Goodbye.

331
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:50,080
Here's the dessert for you as a gift.

332
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,560
You are quite generous.

333
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,560
That's quite unusual.

334
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:53,400
Don't be too touched.

335
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,060
This was left from yesterday.

336
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,180
Help yourself.

337
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:57,400
Ziqiu.

338
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,560
Are you OK?

339
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,660
Nothing wrong with me.

340
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:03,440
I'm fine.

341
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:05,240
Good, I'm just asking.

342
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,720
I'm afraid you might get yourself into a dead end.

343
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,560
If you are here to laugh at me,

344
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:09,020
get lost as fast as you can.

345
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:10,120
How can you

346
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,160
do that to me, He Ziqiu?

347
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,820
I'm just caring about you, OK?

348
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:15,560
I have a rendezvous with someone here

349
00:18:15,560 --> 00:18:16,520
so that your shop will look prosperous,

350
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:17,080
or your store

351
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:17,760
might close down by then.

352
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,120
Well, I'm sorry for disappointing you.

353
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,240
I can keep my store running.

354
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:20,960
Besides, my new products

355
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,360
will be on sale very soon.

356
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,400
Here I am, Mingyue.

357
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,840
You have an appointment with her?

358
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:28,700
Can't I do that?

359
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:30,940
Zhuang Bei.

360
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:36,760
I invited him here to provide legal consultation.

361
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:38,120
All right, what would you like to drink?

362
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,280
I've ordered an ice latte.

363
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:40,560
OK, you go on with your talk,

364
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:41,760
and I'm going to work.

365
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:44,900
Take a seat.

366
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,840
Zhuang Bei, I have an appointment

367
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:51,600
with Ms. Liu at 2:00 p.m.

368
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:52,600
Is that OK with you?

369
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:53,640
Of course not,

370
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,720
I can work on my paperwork here.

371
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,520
Well,

372
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,320
I haven't finished my draft yet.

373
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,120
Mingyue,

374
00:19:00,840 --> 00:19:01,520
Ziqiu looks quite calm

375
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,440
after Li Jianjian

376
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:03,920
chose Ling Xiao,

377
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,880
do you think so?

378
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,200
Yeah, he looks as if nothing has happened.

379
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,160
He came over to our room

380
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,160
and made breakfast for us in the morning.

381
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,040
Yeah.

382
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,840
Anyway,

383
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:15,520
Uncle Li is also his father,

384
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,400
so he wouldn't fall out with Jianjian

385
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:17,920
because Jianjian didn't choose him.

386
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,200
As the old saying goes,

387
00:19:19,560 --> 00:19:20,600
a man's weakness

388
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,450
is only shown late in the night.

389
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,960
But they've grown up together,

390
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:28,300
how come he has such a kind of feeling?

391
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:29,040
I think

392
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:29,760
he can't see anyone else

393
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:30,760
just because

394
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:32,850
they've grown up together.

395
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:34,680
Yep.

396
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,800
Seeing him restrain himself like this,

397
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,120
I feel sorry for him.

398
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,800
It's OK, he's a man.

399
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:42,530
Given some time, he'll be fine.

400
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,700
Here's your latte.

401
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:50,800
Thank you.

402
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:52,280
Help yourselves once your paperwork is finished.

403
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:53,080
I've got to go.

404
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,540
See you at home.

405
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:12,240
A facial massage can only promote blood circulation

406
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:14,300
and increase the elasticity of skin,

407
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,200
but it won't get rid

408
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,320
of wrinkles.

409
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:23,840
Twenty years have passed in the blink of an eye.

410
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,650
I always thought

411
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,280
that it was yesterday

412
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:30,140
when I worked as a shop assistant.

413
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:32,800
I've never thought that I would be getting old.

414
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:34,680
When we were young, we might thought

415
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:36,080
that we wouldn't get old.

416
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:40,160
When I saw Ziqiu that day,

417
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:41,440
I found that

418
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,840
we are really aged women.

419
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,240
He's a nice boy,

420
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,040
just like you.

421
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,060
Don't mention him.

422
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,560
Mei,

423
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:54,760
you are not going to

424
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:57,400
recognize Ziqiu as your son again?

425
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,930
I don't think he holds the grudge against you.

426
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:00,920
Li Haichao brought him up

427
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:02,560
with great efforts,

428
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:05,360
it would be a shame for me to get him back.

429
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:06,960
You see the consequence

430
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,320
of Zhao Huaguang?

431
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:10,760
A man cannot be greedy.

432
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:12,960
But there was no way out for you

433
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,000
back then.

434
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:15,800
You left him there for his sake,

435
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:17,040
didn't you?

436
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,490
No one will believe in this.

437
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:22,940
You are so tough

438
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:25,120
and sturdy.

439
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:26,680
At this age,

440
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:28,680
we look older than the young.

441
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:31,720
You don't have to make it hard for yourself.

442
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:35,760
If you think you are old,

443
00:21:35,760 --> 00:21:37,440
just talk about yourself.

444
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:39,520
I don't think I'm old,

445
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:42,200
and I didn't make it hard for myself either.

446
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,120
Besides,

447
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,880
Dongdong is still young,

448
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,160
so I have to do my best to raise him.

449
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:47,960
You never know

450
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,000
how to give in

451
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:50,960
or yield.

452
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,080
Hello?

453
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:00,650
Are you Dongdong's mom?

454
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:01,800
Come here right now.

455
00:22:01,800 --> 00:22:03,560
Dongdong bit his classmate.

456
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:05,560
OK, I'll be right there.

457
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,040
What's up?

458
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:08,560
I have to go to the kindergarten

459
00:22:08,560 --> 00:22:09,760
Dongdong studies in.

460
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,240
Madam,

461
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:13,440
we reached an agreement before.

462
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,720
If Dongdong attacks others

463
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,200
without any reason again,

464
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:17,520
we can't keep him

465
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:19,200
in our kindergarten anymore.

466
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,760
Dongdong won't

467
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:22,020
attack other children

468
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:24,540
as long as they don't snatch his toys.

469
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:26,560
But these children are still young,

470
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,520
how can we prevent them

471
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,720
from snatching toys?

472
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:31,460
Even teachers cannot keep an eye on them.

473
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,600
Now the parents of other children

474
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:34,440
feel dissatisfied

475
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:35,560
with our kindergarten.

476
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:36,400
We have to

477
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:38,060
keep other children safe too.

478
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:41,040
Yeah, but...

479
00:22:41,040 --> 00:22:41,960
Madam,

480
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,960
honestly, I suggest you

481
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,720
send Dongdong

482
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,450
to a special education school.

483
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,200
Dongdong was not born autistic,

484
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,880
and I've been taking him

485
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,140
to see psychologists.

486
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,320
I understand.

487
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,600
Well, please don't bring Dongdong here

488
00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,260
until he's mentally healthy.

489
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,240
For Dongdong,

490
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:02,320
being in a kindergarten

491
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,920
where he doesn't feel secure

492
00:23:04,280 --> 00:23:06,010
might only worsen his illness.

493
00:23:38,080 --> 00:23:39,760
What's wrong, Dongdong?

494
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:45,400
It's OK, Dongdong.

495
00:23:45,520 --> 00:23:47,320
Let's go have a rest at home for a few days.

496
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,480
We'll be back later, OK?

497
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,130
Put your arms around me.

498
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:53,520
Good boy.

499
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,540
[Experimental Kindergarten]

500
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:04,240
You are Wang Mingxia, right?

501
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,200
Li Xiaoqiang is the defendant.

502
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,400
This is your indictment.

503
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,680
And this is the compensation for mental damage,

504
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:11,400
which is 50,000 yuan.

505
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,320
If you have no question about this,

506
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,520
that's all for today.

507
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:14,920
OK.

508
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,280
Thank you.

509
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:19,160
You are welcome.

510
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:19,760
Thank you.

511
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,090
You are welcome.

512
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,200
This way, please.

513
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:23,740
Don't bother to see me out.

514
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:27,320
Mingyue,

515
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:29,880
it's so nice of you.

516
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,000
You helped them

517
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,330
both on and off the show.

518
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:33,280
No wonder my mom

519
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,640
likes your show so much.

520
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,240
She always says that the reporters of your TV station

521
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:38,100
are beautiful and kind-hearted.

522
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:39,640
That's my duty.

523
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:42,400
Li Jianjian told me

524
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,240
that you planned to study law too

525
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,200
in your high school days.

526
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,560
We almost became colleagues.

527
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:46,880
I wanted to study journalism,

528
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,760
while my mom expected me to study law.

529
00:24:48,760 --> 00:24:50,240
However, I failed in the college entrance examination

530
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,640
and just got less than 550 points

531
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,360
because I was stressed out.

532
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:55,440
You passed the first tier standard?

533
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,000
Yes,

534
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,880
but my mom wanted me to retake high school courses.

535
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,520
I told her that I felt stressed

536
00:24:58,520 --> 00:25:00,000
as soon as I entered the examination room,

537
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:02,120
so retaking courses wouldn't work out.

538
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:03,320
Finally, she gave in

539
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:05,280
and said I should either study journalism

540
00:25:05,280 --> 00:25:05,960
in this city

541
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:06,880
or retake courses

542
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,610
without going out of this city.

543
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:09,920
All parents

544
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:11,040
hope their children

545
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:11,800
to stay with them.

546
00:25:11,800 --> 00:25:13,000
That's quite normal.

547
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:15,130
You were forced to return here too?

548
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:15,880
No.

549
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,880
My parents are glad to see I make decisions on my own.

550
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:18,640
I made up the decision

551
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,040
to stay with them myself.

552
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:20,920
When I was young,

553
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:22,760
my dad ran his business out there,

554
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,640
while my mom had to take care of the family.

555
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,560
Life was hard for both of them.

556
00:25:25,560 --> 00:25:26,040
When they are old,

557
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,370
I hope to stay with them.

558
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,520
It's really nice of your parents.

559
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,480
In my family,

560
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:33,040
my mom is the boss.

561
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:34,720
At the beginning, my mom just wanted me

562
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:35,960
to distinguish myself.

563
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,480
However, after I failed in the college entrance examination,

564
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,760
she gave this up,

565
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,920
and just wanted me to stay with her,

566
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:42,000
hoping me to get married

567
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,640
and have children early.

568
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:45,920
I'm just 25,

569
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:46,880
but she is finding men

570
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:47,920
for me to date.

571
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:49,680
You went to date them?

572
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,560
Yes, I had to, OK?

573
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:08,700
Why did you have a detour to pick me up?

574
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,360
In the future, I'll pick you up every day,

575
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:10,920
OK?

576
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:14,480
Looks like you are in a good mood today.

577
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,880
Anything good happened?

578
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,280
