864
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:04,600
in secret.

865
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:06,490
You should be more careful, OK?

866
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,760
Have you got back the money

867
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,040
you lent to your ex-boyfriend

868
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:10,200
without telling us?

869
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,010
Li Jianjian?

870
00:38:19,240 --> 00:38:20,040
The two of you

871
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:21,480
are so close to each other now

872
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,610
that you even took him to see your tree.

873
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:24,960
How sweet!

874
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:32,640
You seem to be sleepwalking.

875
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,880
Why do you want to know

876
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:35,680
what happened to Ling Xiao in Singapore for no reason?

877
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:37,040
If you do want to know that,

878
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:38,080
just go ask him.

879
00:38:39,960 --> 00:38:41,840
I think my brother Ling Xiao

880
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:44,400
is a little mentally unhealthy.

881
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:44,920
Indeed Ling Xiao

882
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,250
is mentally unhealthy.

883
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,800
You have sharp ears!

884
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,640
I'm telling you,

885
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:50,960
one might be embarrassed

886
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,020
to chat with others

887
00:38:52,040 --> 00:38:53,240
if he or she

888
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,770
isn't mentally unhealthy.

889
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,520
But I think

890
00:38:57,880 --> 00:39:00,280
Ziqiu is the one who's mentally unhealthy.

891
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:03,800
You chose Ling Xiao, and he felt so frustrated.

892
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:04,840
I met him at the door

893
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,800
when I came back.

894
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,080
He was drunk.

895
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,240
He didn't come back

896
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:09,360
until you were back?

897
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:11,400
No. I had an appointment

898
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:13,640
with Zhuang Bei in Ziqiu's coffee shop

899
00:39:13,640 --> 00:39:14,880
to provide legal consultation

900
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,600
for that woman who suffered domestic violence.

901
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:18,640
But he wasn't in the shop in the afternoon.

902
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:22,640
His shop assistant said that their business has been bad in recent days.

903
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:14,080
Jianjian,

904
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:17,120
you are still staying up so late?

905
00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:20,720
Jianjian?

906
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:21,760
Speak.

907
00:40:23,560 --> 00:40:24,320
Dad.

908
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:26,840
What's wrong?

909
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,240
Why are you so low-spirited?

910
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,570
It's like you're dying.

911
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,880
I took a hit.

912
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,570
Tell me. What happened?

913
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,320
Well...

914
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:45,280
Well...

915
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:49,600
I can't tell you now.

916
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,240
I'll tell you later.

917
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:54,460
You're keeping it secret from me?

918
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:58,240
Then why did you call me?

919
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:01,720
I need to be encouraged to face it.

920
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:04,000
I need you to cheer me on

921
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,660
like refueling a car with gas.

922
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,080
You need me to

923
00:41:09,080 --> 00:41:10,560
refuel your car?

924
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:12,480
Don't you

925
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,010
run a gas station yourself?

926
00:41:14,160 --> 00:41:15,440
Don't our whole family

927
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:17,300
always go to your place to refuel?

928
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:21,560
My gas station is running out of gas now.
